%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93/Tho%C3%A1i-c%C6%B0-m%E1%BA%A1n-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-GgXfnqUIZXy4a2oWyv1KmQ">Thoái cư mạn đề kỳ 1 - 退居漫題其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93/author--S-Kylm25PBOdm26_KrpXQ">Tư Không Đồ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Thu%E1%BB%B7-long-ng%C3%A2m-Th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-Ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%E1%BA%A5t-Phu-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-hoa-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-mOiurUYvXkO0XExvBFPyWQ">Thuỷ long ngâm - Thứ vận Chương Chất Phu “Dương hoa từ” - 水龍吟－次韻章質夫楊花詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Th%C6%B0-th%C3%A1n/poem-6E7FIE6gDHSy2UWGhlL-Jg">Thư thán - 書嘆</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tu%C3%BD-ca-h%C3%A0nh-Bi%E1%BB%87t-t%C3%B2ng-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87t-C%E1%BA%A7n-l%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-quy-c%E1%BA%A7n-nh%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1c-khuy%E1%BA%BFn/poem-4WfIEG4ivnwdSAmKNxd6BA">Tuý ca hành - Biệt tòng điệt Cần lạc đệ quy, cần nhất tác khuyến - 醉歌行－別從侄勤落第歸，勤一作勸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
